it-edit (Integrated Terminals Editor)
*************************************

Developer: Eddie Brüggemann

Contact: mrcyberfighter@gmail.com

version: 3.0

Language: C++

Release Time: Sun, 19 Mar 2017 13:52:21 +0100

License: GPLv3

Dependencies:
*************

Required
--------

* gtk+-3.0

* gtksourceview-3.

* vte-2.91.

* sed

* wc

Optionally
----------

* gspell-1.


.. note:: I highly recommend you to install gspell-1 on your system before compiling it-edit.

  You can get it with the ppa gnome3-staging, the DEBIAN sid repository or from source >= Gtk-3.20.

Installation
************

  Simply type:

    $ ./configure
    $ make
    $ sudo make install

  or

    $ ./configure --disable-gspell-1
    $ make
    $ sudo make install

:note: By Mac OS X type: `chmod +x ./install-sh` before making.

Mac OS X
--------

You can get all the required library from the package manager brew:

* gtk+3

* gtk-chtheme

* gtk-mac-integration

* gtksourceview3

* gspell

* adwaita-icon-theme

* vte3

